{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847043325,"sessionID":"ses_28744ed6effecYWaPBNhQAOkVR","part":{"id":"prt_d78bb6cc2001YFklodRE2ynHP7","messageID":"msg_d78bb5cf9001VwMkILYk26eZEz","sessionID":"ses_28744ed6effecYWaPBNhQAOkVR","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_f479d1626f734d46b4fbb845","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-007/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-007/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/workloadmanager  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** L  \n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Implementation Ready)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: Reconciler Framework Setup\n11: \n12: - [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler.go` — define Reconciler struct with client, scheme, log\n13: - [ ] **1.2** Implement `Reconcile(ctx, req)` method — fetch Sandbox, determine action (create/update/delete), execute reconciliation\n14: - [ ] **1.3** Implement `SetupWithManager(mgr)` — register controller with controller-runtime, setup workqueue\n15: - [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/suite_test.go` — setup test environment with envtest\n16: - [ ] **1.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler_suite_test.go` — basic reconcile test\n17: \n18: ---\n19: \n20: ## Phase 2: K8s Client & Informers\n21: \n22: - [ ] **2.1** Add k8s client initialization in `pkg/workloadmanager/client.go` — clientset for Sandbox, Pod, Service, ConfigMap\n23: - [ ] **2.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/informers.go` — setup informers for Sandbox, Pod, Service, ConfigMap\n24: - [ ] **2.3** Implement indexers for efficient lookups — index by sandbox-uid, session-id\n25: - [ ] **2.4** Add `NewReconciler(clusterClient, client, log, scheme)` factory function\n26: - [ ] **2.5** Verify k8s client connectivity in unit tests\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## Phase 3: Create Reconciliation\n31: \n32: - [ ] **3.1** Implement `reconcileCreate` in `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/create.go` — fetch Sandbox and validate spec\n33: - [ ] **3.2** Implement `createPod` — create Pod with ownerReference to Sandbox, set Image, Env, Resources\n34: - [ ] **3.3** Implement `createServices` — create Services if specified in Sandbox spec (ClusterIP/LoadBalancer)\n35: - [ ] **3.4** Implement `createConfigMaps` — create ConfigMaps if specified\n36: - [ ] **3.5** Update Sandbox status to Running after successful creation\n37: - [ ] **3.6** Handle partial creation failures with cleanup\n38: \n39: ---\n40: \n41: ## Phase 4: Update Reconciliation\n42: \n43: - [ ] **4.1** Implement `reconcileUpdate` in `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/update.go` — detect changed fields using resourceVersion\n44: - [ ] **4.2** Implement `updatePod` — patch Pod with new spec (image, env, resources)\n45: - [ ] **4.3** Implement `updateServices` — patch Services if spec changed\n46: - [ ] **4.4** Implement `updateConfigMaps` — patch ConfigMaps if spec changed\n47: - [ ] **4.5** Add field-level diff logging for debugging\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## Phase 5: Delete Reconciliation\n52: \n53: - [ ] **5.1** Implement `reconcileDelete` in `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/delete.go` — handle final cleanup\n54: - [ ] **5.2** Implement `cleanupOwnedResources` — delete Pods, Services, ConfigMaps with ownerReference\n55: - [ ] **5.3** Verify cascade deletion works via ownerReferences\n56: - [ ] **5.4** Handle stuck resources that fail to delete — force delete after grace period expires\n57: \n58: ---\n59: \n60: ## Phase 6: Periodic Sync\n61: \n62: - [ ] **6.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sync.go` — implement periodic reconciliation\n63: - [ ] **6.2** Add sync interval configuration (default 30s) to config\n64: - [ ] **6.3** Implement `syncAllSandboxes` — scan all Sandboxes, check desired spec vs actual cluster resources\n65: - [ ] **6.4** Add drift detection — compare desired state vs actual cluster state\n66: - [ ] **6.5** Implement `repairDrift` — fix any state mismatches\n67: \n68: ---\n69: \n70: ## Phase 7: Status & Conditions\n71: \n72: - [ ] **7.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status.go` — implement `updateStatusConditions`\n73: - [ ] **7.2** Implement Pod status sync — map Pod conditions (PodScheduled, ContainersReady) to Sandbox conditions\n74: - [ ] **7.3** Implement status phase management — Pending/Running/Succeeded/Failed/Unknown\n75: - [ ] **7.4** Add `setStatusPhase(phase)` helper\n76: - [ ] **7.5** Add condition helpers: `setCondition(type, status, reason, message)`\n77: \n78: ---\n79: \n80: ## Phase 8: Error Handling & Retry\n81: \n82: - [ ] **8.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/errors.go` — define reconciler error types\n83: - [ ] **8.2** Implement exponential backoff retry — max 5 retries with delays (1s, 2s, 4s, 8s, 16s)\n84: - [ ] **8.3** Handle transient errors: retry up to 5 times\n85: - [ ] **8.4** Handle permanent errors: set Failed status, emit event, no retry\n86: - [ ] **8.5** Implement conflict handling: fetch latest, re-apply\n87: \n88: ---\n89: \n90: ## Phase 9: Event Recording\n91: \n92: - [ ] **9.1** Integrate k8s event recorder in Reconciler struct\n93: - [ ] **9.2** Emit events for: Create success/failure, Update, Delete, Retry\n94: - [ ] **9.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/events.go` — event emission helpers\n95: - [ ] **9.4** Add event filtering to avoid duplicate events\n96: \n97: ---\n98: \n99: ## Phase 10: Workqueue & Rate Limiting\n100: \n101: - [ ] **10.1** Setup workqueue with rate limiting in `SetupWithManager`\n102: - [ ] **10.2** Configure bucket4j rate limiter: burst 10, rate 10 QPS\n103: - [ ] **10.3** Implement priority: delete > update > create\n104: - [ ] **10.4** Add namespace-scoped rate limiting\n105: - [ ] **10.5** Implement max concurrent reconciles per namespace (default 10)\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ## Phase 11: Metrics & Observability\n110: \n111: - [ ] **11.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/metrics.go` — define Prometheus metrics\n112: - [ ] **11.2** Add `sandbox_reconcile_total` counter with labels: result, namespace\n113: - [ ] **11.3** Add `sandbox_reconcile_duration_seconds` histogram\n114: - [ ] **11.4** Add `sandbox_reconcile_retries_total` counter\n115: - [ ] **11.5** Add `sandbox_workqueue_depth` gauge\n116: - [ ] **11.6** Expose metrics endpoint in workloadmanager (prometheus.io/scrape)\n117: \n118: ---\n119: \n120: ## Phase 12: Health Checks\n121: \n122: - [ ] **12.1** Implement `/healthz/reconciler` health check endpoint\n123: - [ ] **12.2** Check informer sync status (cache synced)\n124: - [ ] **12.3** Report workqueue depth\n125: - [ ] **12.4** Report last reconciliation timestamp\n126: \n127: ---\n128: \n129: ## Phase 13: Unit Tests\n130: \n131: - [ ] **13.1** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/create_test.go` — TestReconcileCreate_Success\n132: - [ ] **13.2** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/create_test.go` — TestReconcileCreate_PodCreation\n133: - [ ] **13.3** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/create_test.go` — TestReconcileCreate_ServiceCreation\n134: - [ ] **13.4** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/update_test.go` — TestReconcileUpdate_DetectChanges\n135: - [ ] **13.5** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/update_test.go` — TestReconcileUpdate_PodPatch\n136: - [ ] **13.6** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/delete_test.go` — TestReconcileDelete_Cleanup\n137: - [ ] **13.7** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_test.go` — TestStatusSync_PodToSandbox\n138: - [ ] **13.8** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_test.go` — TestStatusConditions\n139: - [ ] **13.9** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/error_test.go` — TestRetryWithBackoff\n140: - [ ] **13.10** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/error_test.go` — TestPermanentError_NoRetry\n141: - [ ] **13.11** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sync_test.go` — TestPeriodicSync\n142: \n143: ---\n144: \n145: ## Phase 14: Integration Tests\n146: \n147: - [ ] **14.1** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/e2e_test.go` — E2E create sandbox and verify Pod created\n148: - [ ] **14.2** E2E update sandbox spec and verify Pod updated\n149: - [ ] **14.3** E2E delete sandbox and verify owned resources cleaned up\n150: - [ ] **14.4** E2E reconcile failure and verify status updated to Failed\n151: \n152: ---\n153: \n154: ## Phase 15: Verification\n155: \n156: - [ ] **15.1** `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` — successful compilation\n157: - [ ] **15.2** `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/...` — all unit tests pass\n158: - [ ] **15.3** `go test -race ./pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/...` — no race conditions\n159: - [ ] **15.4** `go vet ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` — no issues\n160: - [ ] **15.5** `golangci-lint run ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` — linter passes\n161: - [ ] **15.6** Test coverage > 50% (`go test -coverprofile=c.out ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`)\n162: \n163: ---\n164: \n165: ## Dependency Graph\n166: \n167: | Task | Depends On |\n168: |------|------------|\n169: | Phase 1 | — (standalone) |\n170: | Phase 2 | Phase 1 |\n171: | Phase 3 | Phase 2 |\n172: | Phase 4 | Phase 3 |\n173: | Phase 5 | Phase 2 |\n174: | Phase 6 | Phase 3 |\n175: | Phase 7 | Phase 3, Phase 4 |\n176: | Phase 8 | Phase 3-7 |\n177: | Phase 9 | Phase 1 |\n178: | Phase 10 | Phase 1 |\n179: | Phase 11 | Phase 1 |\n180: | Phase 12 | Phase 1 |\n181: | Phase 13 | Phase 1-12 |\n182: | Phase 14 | Phase 13 |\n183: | Phase 15 | Phase 13-14 |\n184: \n185: ---\n186: \n187: ## References\n188: \n189: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-007/delta-spec.md`\n190: - Design: ST-3 completed (Implementation Ready)\n191: - Related AR: AR-005 (Sandbox 创建处理器), AR-006 (Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理)\n192: - Kubernetes Controller Runtime: https://book.kubebuilder.io/\n\n(End of file - total 192 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/workloadmanager  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** L  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Implementation Ready)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Reconciler Framework Setup\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler.go` — define Reconciler struct with client, scheme, log\n- [ ] **1.2** Implement `Reconcile(ctx, req)` method — fetch Sandbox, determine action (create/update/delete), execute reconciliation\n- [ ] **1.3** Implement `SetupWithManager(mgr)` — register controller with controller-runtime, setup workqueue\n- [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/suite_test.go` — setup test environment with envtest\n- [ ] **1.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler_suite_test.go` — basic reconcile test\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: K8s Client & Informers","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-007/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775847043300,"end":1775847043320}}}}
